 Slide 12: Loss Curve Analysis

 Title: Training Dynamics (Epochs 1–10)

 Validation Loss Trends:
 - All CNNs show consistent loss reduction
 - ResNet-50: Steepest drop but plateaus early (overfitting)
 - DenseNet-121: Steady, sustained improvement
 - EfficientNet-B0: Competitive with DenseNet
 - ResNeXt-50: Slower start but best long-term performance

