 - ResNet-50: Drops to 0.99 by epoch 10 (memorization)
 - DenseNet-121: Higher training loss (4.24) but better val performance
 - ResNeXt-50: Maintains higher training loss (due to multi-cell-type complexity)

 ConvNeXt & ViT: Plateaued near random loss (~7.0) — failed to learn

